public interface GenericRepository<T,PK extends java.io.Serializable>

GenericRepository is an interface, which avoids to repeat defining CRUD methods for Data Access Objects again and again. For detailed information compare http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/java/library/j-genericdao.html

Author:
Thomas Feiner
